doc_summary_long: Santa Monica High School canceled an anti-drug program after parents learned that it is affiliated with the church of Scientology. The Foundation for a Drug Free World recently held three assemblies at Santa Monica High School. But the principal scrubbed the rest of the series on substance abuse prevention. Parents were upset after they got wind the Church of Scientology sponsored the talks.
doc_summary_short: Santa Monica High School canceled an anti-drug program after parents learned that it is affiliated with the church of Scientology.
doc_title: Santa Monica High School Ends Anti-Drug Program After Parents Find Scientology Link
